text: Vasily Ivanovich Vlasenko was a middle-distance runner from USSR. Vlasenko competed at the 1956 Summer Olympics. He was born on 10 January 1928 and died on 5 August 2020.Vasily Vlasenko == References == Category:1928 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Middle-distance runners Category:Olympians for the Soviet Union
